    <entry>
      <title>PS 2025 软件下载安装教程</title>
      <link href="/2025/04/26/PS%202025%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2025/04/26/PS%202025%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Photoshop 2025 v26.5是Adobe公司推出的一款功能强大的图像处理软件，在平面设计、摄影后期、UI设计等众多领域应用广泛。它显著升级了ACR至17.2版本，色彩处理更加精准，还加入了神经滤镜的离线安装包，借助Adobe Sensei机器学习技术，能实现智能肖像重塑、照片修复、超级缩放图像等复杂任务。此外，软件优化了运行效率，图像加载速度大幅提升，在不同硬件配置下都能保持流畅运行。其新增的刺绣滤镜、对象选择人物功能以及增强型框架工具等，进一步丰富了创作功能，让用户的创意表达更加自由和便捷。</p><h2>安装教程</h2><p>1.下载完成后，鼠标右击【Photoshop 2025 v26.5】压缩包，选择【解压至此处】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-62781 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-53.jpg" width="815" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-53.jpg 815w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-53-768x597.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 815px) 100vw, 815px" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图" data-mwl-img-id="62781" mwl-index="0"></p><p>2.鼠标右击【autoplay】安装程序，点击【以管理员身份运行】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62782 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-53.jpg" width="815" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-53.jpg 815w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-53-768x597.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 815px) 100vw, 815px" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图1" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图1" data-mwl-img-id="62782" mwl-index="1"></p><p>3.点击【Install】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62783 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/3-53.jpg" width="450" height="679" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图2" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图2" data-mwl-img-id="62783" mwl-index="2"></p><p>4.点击文件夹图标可以修改软件安装位置，点击【继续】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62784 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/4-53.jpg" width="448" height="677" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图3" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图3" data-mwl-img-id="62784" mwl-index="3"></p><p>5.软件安装中…</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62785 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/5-52.jpg" width="448" height="677" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图4" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图4" data-mwl-img-id="62785" mwl-index="4"></p><p>6.显示安装完成，点击【关闭】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62786 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/6-51.jpg" width="448" height="677" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图5" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图5" data-mwl-img-id="62786" mwl-index="5"></p><p>7.创建桌面快捷方式：①点击桌面任务栏中的【开始图标】&gt;点击【所有应用】②将【Adobe Photoshop 2025】图标拖到电脑桌面</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62787 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/7-50.jpg" width="813" height="784" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/7-50.jpg 813w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/7-50-768x741.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 813px) 100vw, 813px" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图6" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图6" data-mwl-img-id="62787" mwl-index="6"></p><p>8.双击桌面的【Adobe Photoshop 2025】图标启动软件</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62788 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/8-49.jpg" width="317" height="240" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图7" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图7" data-mwl-img-id="62788" mwl-index="7"></p><p>9.安装完成</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62789 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-36-1024x492.jpg" width="1024" height="492" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-36-1024x492.jpg 1024w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-36-768x369.jpg 768w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-36-1536x739.jpg 1536w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-36-2048x985.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" title="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图8" alt="Photoshop 2025 v26.5插图8" data-mwl-img-id="62789" mwl-index="8"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
