      <title>MAYA2026 软件安装教程</title>
      <link href="/2025/04/26/MAYA2026%20%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2025/04/26/MAYA2026%20%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Autodesk Maya 2026是一款专业的三维软件，主要用于电影、电视、游戏等行业中创建逼真的角色、宏大的场景和炫酷的特效。它拥有强大的多边形和NURBS建模工具，能创建各种复杂的三维模型。在动画制作方面，关键帧、非线性和运动捕捉等功能可以让角色栩栩如生，新的“Animate in Context”功能更是能让动画师在处理镜头时，直接在Maya内检视相关镜头，提升剪辑连贯性和动画制作的精准度。特效模拟上，Bifrost更新至2.13.0.0版本，其FLIP解算器提供更灵活的流體模擬功能，还支持自适应分辨率和粒子泡沫模拟等。此外，Maya 2026强化了USD整合，支持新版USD 0.31并加入光源连结功能，方便跨平台、跨应用的场景资料交换。同时，通过集成的开放标准如OpenUSD，以及与Unreal Live Link等插件的配合，能有效改善团队协作效率。</p><h2>安装教程</h2><p>1.下载完成后，鼠标右击【Maya 2026】压缩包，选择【解压至此处】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63188 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-79.jpg" width="792" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-79.jpg 792w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-79-768x615.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px" title="Maya 2026插图" alt="Maya 2026插图" data-mwl-img-id="63188" mwl-index="0"></p><p>2.正在提取 Maya 2026 Windows db 安装程序，稍等加载中</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63190 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/3-79.jpg" width="462" height="202" title="Maya 2026插图1" alt="Maya 2026插图1" data-mwl-img-id="63190" mwl-index="1"></p><p>3.鼠标右击安装程序，点击【以管理员身份运行】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63189 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-79.jpg" width="792" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-79.jpg 792w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-79-768x615.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px" title="Maya 2026插图2" alt="Maya 2026插图2" data-mwl-img-id="63189" mwl-index="2"></p><p>4.点击【运行安装程序】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63191 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/4-79.jpg" width="513" height="152" title="Maya 2026插图3" alt="Maya 2026插图3" data-mwl-img-id="63191" mwl-index="3"></p><p>5.软件许可同意，勾选【我同意使用条款】，然后点击【下一步】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63193 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/6-75.jpg" width="700" height="522" title="Maya 2026插图4" alt="Maya 2026插图4" data-mwl-img-id="63193" mwl-index="4"></p><p>6.选择安装位置，点击【…】进去更改安装位置（注意：更改安装位置不能带中文或特殊符号），然后下一步</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63194 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/7-74.jpg" width="700" height="522" title="Maya 2026插图5" alt="Maya 2026插图5" data-mwl-img-id="63194" mwl-index="5"></p><p>7.选择其他组件，默认勾选，然后点击安装</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63195 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/8-73.jpg" width="700" height="522" title="Maya 2026插图6" alt="Maya 2026插图6" data-mwl-img-id="63195" mwl-index="6"></p><p>8.正在安装中，请耐心稍等</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63196 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-57.jpg" width="700" height="522" title="Maya 2026插图7" alt="Maya 2026插图7" data-mwl-img-id="63196" mwl-index="7"></p><p>9.如果安装中途弹出窗口，点击X关闭即可（没有弹出则忽略）</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63198 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11-46.jpg" width="860" height="500" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11-46.jpg 860w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11-46-768x447.jpg 768w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11-46-600x350.jpg 600w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11-46-380x220.jpg 380w" sizes="(max-width: 860px) 100vw, 860px" title="Maya 2026插图8" alt="Maya 2026插图8" data-mwl-img-id="63198" mwl-index="8"></p><p>10.Maya 2026安装成功，点击【X】关闭</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63197 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10-48.jpg" width="700" height="522" title="Maya 2026插图9" alt="Maya 2026插图9" data-mwl-img-id="63197" mwl-index="9"></p><p>11.打开破解文件夹，然后里面有2个破解方法，大家自行选择（而接下来我们将以最简单的破解方法1为例进行讲解，破解方法2中有操作方法，想要以这个方法破解的请跟着说明操作）</p><p>双击打开【破解方式1】文件夹，全选文件夹中的所有文件，点击【复制】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63199 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/12-44.jpg" width="792" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/12-44.jpg 792w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/12-44-768x615.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px" title="Maya 2026插图10" alt="Maya 2026插图10" data-mwl-img-id="63199" mwl-index="10"></p><p>12.鼠标右击桌面的【Maya 2026】，点击【打开文件所在的位置】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63200 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13-43.jpg" width="330" height="508" title="Maya 2026插图11" alt="Maya 2026插图11" data-mwl-img-id="63200" mwl-index="11"></p><p>13.鼠标在空白处右击，点击【粘贴】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63201 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/14-41.jpg" width="792" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/14-41.jpg 792w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/14-41-768x615.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px" title="Maya 2026插图12" alt="Maya 2026插图12" data-mwl-img-id="63201" mwl-index="12"></p><p>14.点击【替换目标中的文件】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63202 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/15-29.jpg" width="449" height="308" title="Maya 2026插图13" alt="Maya 2026插图13" data-mwl-img-id="63202" mwl-index="13"></p><p>15.双击桌面的【Maya 2026】图标启动软件</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63203 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/16-23.jpg" width="314" height="229" title="Maya 2026插图14" alt="Maya 2026插图14" data-mwl-img-id="63203" mwl-index="14"></p><p>16.安装完成</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-63204 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/17-18.jpg" width="1915" height="1229" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/17-18.jpg 1915w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/17-18-1024x657.jpg 1024w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/17-18-768x493.jpg 768w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/17-18-1536x986.jpg 1536w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/17-18-300x193.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1915px) 100vw, 1915px" title="Maya 2026插图15" alt="Maya 2026插图15" data-mwl-img-id="63204" mwl-index="15"></p>]]></content>
      
      
